title: lost all my champs
body: i typed in a new username when i signed in and i lost everything i had on my account, how do i resign into my account with all my champs/mast/runes? completely lost here. THANKS

replies.body:
We don't reset accounts for any reason, so you're most likely logging into the wrong account. Use our [**NA Username Recovery Page**](https://account.leagueoflegends.com/na/en/forgot-username) in order to recover all usernames tied to your email.

Let me know if this helped.
my previous account name was redeyed summoner
